Definition: anesthesia of the lower half of the body
Example: caused by injury to the spinal cord or by injecting an anesthetic beneath the arachnoid membrane that surrounds the spinal cord
Synonyms: spinal_anaesthesia, spinal, regional_anesthesia, anesthesia, of, the, lower, half, body, caused, by, injury, to, cord, or, injecting, an, anesthetic, beneath, arachnoid, membrane, that, surrounds
Category: noun.state
